Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要砍掉…『七乡』！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是元老院的一致意见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七乡』的开花给世界带来了多大危机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在危机已经变成现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便不可固守不出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 这个城镇…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随着『七乡』的毁灭而消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以一个城镇的代价便可以拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个…城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这个城镇毁灭了 妖怪们会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从円神出现开始 你以为过了多长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间没有做出成果的是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民的撤离就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是作为町长最后的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:36.85,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)}{\pos(475,325)}荆棘之路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋元老院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前花刚刚开 这次又是这种奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会又是你们做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个城镇到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 町长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是明摆着的吗 没关…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关…系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 元老院准备想要切断『七乡』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌乱的冲进去又会被土地神干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界已经被破坏的现在 不是还有办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束 没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说过了的 其他的妖怪优先治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 『调率』是非常危险的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍错一点 秋名会和送归的妖怪一起到那个世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了就好 今后…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被『调率』的妖怪会非常痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 并不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 『调率』是修正人界和妖界的次元偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让妖怪更加方便进入那边的世界而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比被灭杀要轻松很多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为那就如字面意思是杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃华 你没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 树里帮我戴上的新枷似乎很奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 姬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡逻中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不会犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好长好长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很长 但是很暖和的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要安静一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬 已经可以说话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤痕…留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上这个就看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名 银
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是稍微有点长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 所以才说的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿给我 帮你修短
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身行李是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 正准备去避难…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好在城外有栖身的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避难？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从生活相谈事务所的人那听到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「为了以防万一 请准备好」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 空地或者体育馆都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊 对不起 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托过了 但是果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 说到收容妖怪 什么地方的城镇都会讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会有这城镇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可没时间消沉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无处可去的居民还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得下了避难的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有指示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是存在可能性 为了万一的时候做准备而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是町长不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町长怎么能不优先考虑居民的安全呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只是为了万一 秋名也这样说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍 抱歉 树里那里人手不够 去帮忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃城镇而逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有说这种事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听从元老院的摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把居民从城镇撤离出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元老院会立刻砍掉『七乡』的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要为了不砍掉而留下居民吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是现在这样做会给居民带来多余的不安而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上存在危险的可能 怎么会是无用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想要逃避而已不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从円神身边逃避不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没有客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道城镇安全了 就马上会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快点逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神吗 已经刻不容缓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始切断『七乡』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『调率』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去 回小姐那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点程度 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『八彩』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在骚乱之中已经被对方得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从外部送入妖力 已经完全把『七乡』吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方动了脑筋的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖力这东西的话 将其增辐也能从远处进行传送
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和电波一个道理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八重大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随她去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬她一个人没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这点程度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这点程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『火焰喷射器』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物由我们来对付
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 把姬带到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？故障？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』 哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了 总之…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用…我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『囲』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终段『大花火』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我…由我亲手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『弹弹弹弹弹弹弹弹弹弹弹弹』
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又被大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『弹弹弹弹弹弹弹弹弹弹弹弹』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快送到树里小姐那去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还说再开心一会的 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下已成定局了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地神不是无法离开自己负责的土地的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然从那么远的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你已经放弃了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是龙的化身 伤势并没有那么重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过所积累疲劳也并不寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站到现在也只能用不可思议来形容了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她一直都在练功…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 生命倒无危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时休息下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来后一定是这种表情就跑外面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别阻止她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我必须去看看其他患者了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬好可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部自己来背负
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元老院没察觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖力将力量限制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要砍也砍不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言叶 城镇里离『七乡』最远的地方是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中心部 元老院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 请到元老院避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是管理城镇的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间说明了 这里很危险 大家快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是樱真町『七乡』即将开花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立即去元老院避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请避难 『七乡』的开花是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢走 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃华你不用来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是全部人员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面还有一人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要叫她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去找姬定会碰钉子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树里小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她一定在等你哦 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没忘过这天花板了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从这伤之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实什么都没改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样也是想努力下的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽全力练习 公务 巡逻 都是一心一意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 还是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙枪也用不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦有什么情况 也都是让秋名你们出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为町长 为人所爱 为城镇所爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被龙所爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为町长 作为町长却…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银的事 我也不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢银啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我必须要保护城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为町长本不应该说这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最差劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽给大家带来痛苦 自己却什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该如何是好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起保护城镇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥说过的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与秋名 与姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来保护城镇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不静养是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么艰巨的任务 不会那么快就结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了 但现在就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要姬的力量的时候一定会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 能帮我按摩下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.21,0:23:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 客人身体好僵哦 凝固的8 BEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当神也有很多烦心事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.71,0:23:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好想了解下神仙大人哦 讲来听听吧 讲来听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.13,0:23:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 下回是我的「不准出手事」的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.71,0:24:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 烦躁死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着按下腰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神也会积累呢 赘肉
